<head>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "bootstrap3.0", :media => "all" %>
</head>

<div class='container-width'>
  <div class="row bg-white" >
    <div class="col-md-7 col-xs-7" id="counter">
      <%= image_tag("/assets/biker/newbiker11.jpg", :class => "img-responsive home-biker-height") %>
      <%= image_tag("/assets/biker/kickstarter.png", :class => "img-responsive", :id => "sticker") %>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-5 col-xs-5">

      <div class="row header-title">
        HelmetBuds Are Coming
      </div>
      <div class="row header-subtitle">
        <nav class="hidden-xs"> Smart Earphones for Riders </nav>
      </div>

      <div class= "row">
  	    <div class="features-margin">
  	        <div class="col-md-3 col-xs-3">

              <div class="mytooltip"><%= image_tag("/assets/biker/biker-icon.jpg",  :class => "img-responsive") %>
                <span class="mytooltiptext left-tip">
                  We designed everything based on feedback from hundreds of riders like yourself. Our earbuds, don’t fall out while riding and they fit in <br> your helmet. Wear them on the ride or at the gym. <br> Use our wireless remote without taking your hands off the handlebar.
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
        
  	        <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-4 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-offset-1">
              <div class="mytooltip"><%= image_tag("/assets/biker/ear-shield-icon.jpg",  :class => "img-responsive") %>
                <span class="mytooltiptext center-tip center-font">
                  Studies* show, only 15 minutes of Riding can do <span class='feature-text'>permanent damage </span>to your hearing and even helmets don't cut off enough wind noise. Don't lose your hearing. We designed our earbuds to protect your hearing. As a result, you can hear every beat at any speed. <br> <span class='small-font'> *http://www.hearingtestlabs.com/motorcycle.htm & https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC539364/ </span>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-4">
              <div class="mytooltip"><%= image_tag("/assets/biker/hear_stuff_ icon.jpg",  :class => "img-responsive") %>
                <span class="mytooltiptext right-tip">
                  Isolation keeps unwanted road noise out. Our intelligent software 
                  allows you to hear Horns, Sirens and other important sounds. Our 
                  beats feel real. We source our speakers from a company with 
                  decades of experience. It’s audiophile level sound.
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
  	    </div>
      </div>

      <div class= "row">
          <div class="col-md-3 col-xs-3 ">
              <nav class="hidden-xs feature-text"> 
                For The Rider
              </nav>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-4 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-offset-1">
            <nav class="hidden-xs feature-text"> Avoid Hearing <br> Damage </nav>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-4">
            <nav class="hidden-xs feature-text">&nbsp;Hear The <br> Important Stuff </nav>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">

      <div class="form-wrap clearfix <%= "ended" if Rails.application.config.ended %>">
        <% if Rails.application.config.ended %>
          <%= render "users/campaign_ended" %>
        <% else %>
          <%= render "users/campaign_ongoing" %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>